These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, asparagus
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, card-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, spy
1. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
2. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
3. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | mirinda      |
| Food          | asparagus | cucumber    |
| Hobby         | card-games   | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | spy      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, designer
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, subway
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
3. the designer is not to the right of the fisherman##8
4. the person driving the scooter is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | fanta        | 7up    |
| Hobby       | card-games         | sudoku |
| Job         | designer | fisherman   |
| Transport   | scooter               | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, disaster
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, gospel
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: hamster, snake
1. the argentine is in an odd position##4
2. the egyptian is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama       | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | gospel    |
| Nationality   | argentine | egyptian |
| Pet           | hamster        | snake   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, librarian
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, australian
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | video-games  |
| Job           | librarian  | bartender |
| Nationality   | australian | dutch   |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | quad-bike |

