2. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
3. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
4. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
5. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Food        | corn | avocado            |
| Hobby       | collecting | rock-climbing              |
| Job         | security-guard  | architect |
| Transport   | bus     | bike         |

